    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【多人游戏】</strong> <br><strong><u>多个方法开启4人合作游戏</u></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本地 / 线上通过房间邀请码找到4个人一起</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/09b08672c263b7ba7dfd02ac71f936d2.poster.avif?t=1746668625\" width=800 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/09b08672c263b7ba7dfd02ac71f936d2.webm?t=1746668625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/09b08672c263b7ba7dfd02ac71f936d2.mp4?t=1746668625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果1个人玩或凑不齐4个人，可以摇一摇大厅的铃铛寻找线上玩家组队</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/458bcf4794f8a1635cb784918dd0e99c.poster.avif?t=1746668625\" width=800 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/458bcf4794f8a1635cb784918dd0e99c.webm?t=1746668625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/458bcf4794f8a1635cb784918dd0e99c.mp4?t=1746668625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还可以开启“双人模式”通过一个手柄控制两个角色</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/0eab4f367af2f3d01fd12d2ea66a1627.avif?t=1746668625\" width=602 height=288 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【游戏机制】</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >方块动物本身不能移动，需要利用地形和朋友来旋转身体</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/1db649b8a66cc2cb488a1a57dbb55eaf.poster.avif?t=1746668625\" width=800 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/1db649b8a66cc2cb488a1a57dbb55eaf.webm?t=1746668625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/1db649b8a66cc2cb488a1a57dbb55eaf.mp4?t=1746668625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【扭蛋和地图】</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >金币可以用在扭蛋机上解锁装饰和家具，也会得到印章来解锁物品和新地图</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地图是随机选取，其中还有2v2的特殊关卡哦！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/25c2cf756dd4c9e03122567a8c0df3e4.avif?t=1746668625\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras_big/25c2cf756dd4c9e03122567a8c0df3e4.avif?t=1746668625 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【其他功能】</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以通过快捷键发送指定的可爱语音来进行互动</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >其他玩家家园中的物品可以在当前组队中被租用</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/ce0f950743092b3e82b3b4082f11b894.poster.avif?t=1746668625\" width=800 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/ce0f950743092b3e82b3b4082f11b894.webm?t=1746668625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/ce0f950743092b3e82b3b4082f11b894.mp4?t=1746668625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
